             <p id="Overview" style="font-family: 'Book Antiqua'; font-size: x-large; font-weight: bolder; font-style: inherit; font-variant: normal; text-transform: none; color: #000000; text-decoration: underline">OVERVIEW</p>
<h3 style="color: #CC0000">HOTEL FOREST GREEN </h3>      
Hotel Forest Green, a 4 star property, is praised for exhibiting the perfect mix of gracious hospitality, style and luxury. The hotel is owned and managed by Singal Dewan Properties. The hotel is also equipped with all modern day amenities to meet the requirements of both business and leisure travelers. The rooms are well-appointed and equipped with amentias that enhance the comfort level of the guests. The hotel also features business facilities that make it an appropriate venue for various business meetings, launch parties, conferences, exhibitions, auctions, etc. The hotel also has an on-site dining facility, where the guests can enjoy an array of delicious culinary delights.    
<h3 style="color: #CC0000">HOTEL THONGSAL  </h3>
Thongsal resort is nestled in the quiet beauty of Leh and is spread over 3 acres of natural land. This boutique resort offers luxurious accommodations with world-class amenities for a memorable and delightful stay. The hotel is only 1.5 km from the city’s center and lies in close proximity to Gomang Stupa and Mahabodhi Meditation Centre.
The hotel offers splendid views of the Shanti Stupa and the surrounding snow-capped mountains. A golf course is present on the hotel grounds where the guests can get some golf practice done.  A host of services are offered for the guests’ convenience including laundry and ironing services, safety deposit box, bicycle rental, games room, parking on site, Wi-Fi connectivity, souvenir shop, currency exchange,, airport transfer (chargeable), room service, concierge and doctor-on-call. The hotel’s 24 rooms are stylishly furnished and categorized into super deluxe rooms, Deluxe Rooms and Standard rooms. All the rooms are centrally heated.
Dining options include Tingmo restaurant, a bar and a coffee shop called café. Thongsal Resort is the recipient of the prestigious Certificate of Excellence from TripAdvisor for the year 2014.
<h3 style="color: #CC0000">THE PANGONG HOTEL</h3>
The Pangong is one of the A class hotels in Leh and is widely favored for its comforts and hospitality. The hotel is situated just 4.9 km from the Leh airport while the local market is just a 2 minute walk away. The guests can access airlines office, taxi stand, banks and ATMs all at walking distance from the hotel. Among the various facilities and services provided by the hotel are complimentary airport transfers, car rentals (surcharge), currency exchange, travel assistance, laundry facility, internet access (surcharge), doctor on call, uninterrupted power supply and spacious car parking. The hotel also organizes sightseeing tours, trekking trips and cultural programs on request. Guests can visit places of aesthetic significance like Leh Palace, Thiksey Monastery, Shey Palace, Pangong Lake, Shanti Stupa and Khardung La Pass. The hotel offers a serene and pleasant environment for the utmost relaxation of the guests.

<h3 style="color: #CC0000">HOTEL LASERMO</h3>
Located at a short distance of about 4.7 km from the Leh Airport, Hotel Lasermo is a deluxe hotel that provides a wonderful retreat among nature. The hotel is a union of Ladakhi culture and contemporary luxury that is evident from its remarkable architecture and impeccable hospitality. One here, take time to visit the amazing monasteries, indulge in trekking or just wander around the town. Some of the places of attraction such as Thiksey Monastery, Shey Palace, Gurudwara Pathar Sahib, Deksit Monastery, Shanti Stupa and Nubra Valley are close by.  The hotel offers numerous services and facilities which include conference hall, currency exchange, doctor on call, airport transfer (surcharge), travel assistance, taxi / car hire (surcharge), laundry services, pool table, shopping mall, parking facilities and 24 hour front desk. The lush green gardens amidst the mountains are a breathtaking sight in itself. The hotel has been a host to many people from the Indian film fraternity which has highly appreciated its genial hospitality and services.

